{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/LogoSoR_ALT.gif?t=1739391973\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>We are rats circling the ruins of great civilizations. All we have are our songs and the dream that they will not fade away too soon.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/line.png?t=1739391973\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/SoR_01.gif?t=1739391973\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Wreckage is an ever-changing labyrinth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Those who live here stick to their burrows, settlements, and hideouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But there are madmen who abandon safety to venture into the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Madmen like you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/line.png?t=1739391973\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/SoR_02.gif?t=1739391973\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Songs of Rats is a roguelike RPG in which you will delve into a mysterious Wreckland filled with secrets of long-gone civilizations.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Develop your character and gather a team</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face the changing world and its challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the dark secrets of fallen civilizations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face strange, human and inhuman enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SURVIVE!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pet your faithful dog!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DEMO VERSION LIMITATIONS:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only a portion of one of the two scenarios is available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Limited Sandbox mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No game save option.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">English language only.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fight for your life!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Face real nightmares!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find or lose all your hope!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/line.png?t=1739391973\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/dol.gif?t=1739391973\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739391973","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739391973","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/7508de75a59ca941a4c838d53120c678fafbff54/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739391973","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/7508de75a59ca941a4c838d53120c678fafbff54/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739391973","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309930/extras/LogoSoR_ALT.gif?t=1739391973\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>We are rats circling the ruins of great civilizations. All we have are our songs and th